What is new in OAT?

  • OAT.RDFStore ( rdfstore.js)
  • OAT.RDF ( rdf.js) and OAT.N3 ( n3.js) parsers
  • new OAT.Instant() ( instant.js)
  • List of Obsolete Calls
  • OAT.Event and OAT.Style objects ( loader.js)
  • OAT.Browser properties ( loader.js)
  • reworked DAV Browser ( dav.js) with richer and more straightforward API
  • new OAT.AJAX ( ajax2.js) instead of OAT.Ajax ( ajax.js )
